# kramdown2 Converter

## Introduction

This converter converts a kramdown2 element tree into a kramdown2 document and supports all available
element types. This converter, together with the [HTML parser](../parser/html.html), can be used to
convert HTML documents to kramdown2 documents.

Another use would be to format a badly styled kramdown2 document (i.e. one with wrapped lines,
multiple different indentations used in one list, ...).


